# Barter — Architecture Quick Reference

## Monorepo
- `apps/api` — NestJS 11, Prisma 6, PostgreSQL, Meilisearch, Socket.IO
- `apps/web` — Next.js 16, React 19, Tailwind 4, lucide-react
- Root: npm workspaces, `concurrently`, docker-compose (postgres:16 + meili v1.11)

## API Modules (`apps/api/src/`)
| Module | Key files | Endpoints prefix |
|--------|-----------|------------------|
| auth | controller, service, jwt.strategy | `/auth` |
| categories | controller, service | `/categories` |
| listings | controller, service, ranking, haversine, text-similarity | `/listings` |
| search | controller, meilisearch.service, synonyms | `/search` |
| favorites | controller, service | `/favorites` |
| chats | controller, service, gateway (Socket.IO) | `/chats` |
| reviews | controller, service | `/reviews` |
| users | controller, service | `/users` |
| analytics | controller, service | `/analytics` |
| presence | controller, service | `/presence` |
| prisma | service, exception filter | — |

## Data Model (Prisma)
Models: User, Category, Listing (lat/lon, attributes JSON), ListingImage (sha256), ListingPromotion, ListingReport, Favorite, Chat, ChatUser, Message (mediaUrl), SellerReview, UserBehaviorEvent.
Enums: ListingStatus (ACTIVE/PENDING/BLOCKED/SOLD/ARCHIVED), PromotionType (TOP/VIP/XL), AppTheme, MessageMediaType, UserBehaviorEventType.

## Auth
JWT in cookie `token` + Bearer header. Secret from `JWT_SECRET`. 30d expiry. Passport strategy.

## Web Routes (`apps/web/src/app/`)
`/` home, `/auth`, `/new`, `/listing/[id]`, `/seller/[id]`, `/favorites`, `/messages`, `/profile`, `/profile/settings`, `/profile/reviews`, `/profile/orders`

## Integration
Web → API via Next.js rewrites (same-origin). Port 3000 (web), 3001 (API).
